contents.text: Welcome to 23andMe in South Bay, offering you over 125 personalized ancestry, health, and trait reports.
For ancestry insights and heritage reports, press 1.
To speak with a genetic counselor about your ancestry results, press 1.
Please hold while we connect you to a genetic counseling specialist.

navigationGoals: I need to discuss my ancestry results with a genetic counselor.
Speak with a genetic counselor to explore my family’s military ancestry and heritage.
Connect with a counselor to analyze my autosomal admixture percentages and haplogroup assignment
I need to speak with a genetic counselor to help me understand my ancestry results.
Talk with a counselor to understand the statistical breakdown of my ancestry results.

contents.text: For assistance with your DNA kit or sample collection, press 2.
Please hold while we connect you to our sample support team.

navigationGoals: I need help troubleshooting and completing my DNA sample kit.
Get assistance with collecting and returning my 23andMe DNA sample kit correctly.
Resolve a sample registration error and get guidance on my DNA kit collection protocol
I’m having trouble with my DNA kit and need step-by-step help collecting my sample.
Get detailed instructions on how to properly collect and send my DNA sample.

contents.text: For health and trait report inquiries, press 2.
To discuss your health report findings with a genetic counselor, press 1.
Please hold while we connect you to a health counseling specialist.

navigationGoals: I want to review my health report findings with a genetic counseling specialist.
Discuss my health report findings with a genetic counselor to understand service-related risks.
Consult a specialist about my polygenic risk score for cardiovascular disease
I’d like to discuss my health report findings with a genetic counselor and get advice.
Discuss the probability-based risk assessments in my health report with a genetic counselor.

contents.text: For help interpreting your trait reports, press 2.
Please hold while we connect you to our traits support team.

navigationGoals: I need assistance interpreting my genetic trait reports.
Clarify my trait report details—like muscle composition and metabolism—for my fitness regimen.
Get help interpreting the functional impact of my LCT gene variant on lactose intolerance phenotype
I need assistance interpreting my trait reports and understanding what they mean for me.
Understand the genetic basis of my trait reports, such as enzyme-related characteristics.
